17                                             
18                                             # The module exits under a #line directive naming another file, as Template
19                                             # Toolkit's generated parsers do.  The require-tree capture identifies the
20                                             # tree by its own first cop, not the last statement executed, so the
21                                             # top-level statements above stay covered even though the last cop is filed
22                                             # elsewhere.  This return belongs to Parser.yp and is filtered from the
23                                             # report.
